edit, and delete posts</p></li><li><p>Assign tags and categories</p></li><li><p>Rich text editing with Quill Editor<br></p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Cover &amp; Description</strong></p><ul class=\\\"cherry-list__default\\\"><li><p>Each post supports a cover image (upload or URL)</p></li><li><p>Short descriptions for post previews<br></p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Tag System</strong></p><ul class=\\\"cherry-list__default\\\"><li><p>Posts can have multiple tags (e.g., Vue, React, Python, Travel, Food)</p></li><li><p>Tag-based fil', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}', 0, NULL, '2025-10-01 15:18:34');
INSERT INTO `sys_oper_log` (`oper_id`, `title`, `business_type`, `method`, `request_method`, `operator_type`, `oper_name`, `dept_name`, `oper_url`, `oper_ip`, `oper_location`, `oper_param`, `json_result`, `status`, `error_msg`, `oper_time`) VALUES (558, '文章管理', 1, 'com.zaaac.cms.blog.controller.CmsBlogController.add()', 'POST', 1, 'Zac', NULL, '/cms/blog', '134.195.146.217', 'XX XX', '{\"tagIds\":[30],\"title\":\"Portfolio with React and Three.js\",\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<div data-inline-code-theme=\\\"red\\\" data-code-block-theme=\\\"tomorrow-night\\\"><p data-lines=\\\"1\\\" data-type=\\\"p\\\" data-sign=\\\"d345b88afdcd7e3f6962c1abade47d5c1\\\" class=\\\"\\\"><strong>Content:</strong></p><p data-lines=\\\"2\\\" data-type=\\\"p\\\" data-sign=\\\"7e2daa804fbc9288547811cbbab8600a2\\\">When I started designing my personal portfolio, I wanted to create something that went beyond a static list of projects and experiences. Instead of just presenting text and images, I envisioned a website that could showcase my creativity, technical skills, and love for interactive design. That’s how this <strong>Portfolio · Particles Effect</strong> project was born.</p><h3 data-lines=\\\"2\\\" data-sign=\\\"0604b9c9d2090367a8c49166e24d9504\\\" id=\\\"-project-overview\\\"><a href=\\\"#-project-overview\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\"></a>🌌 Project Overview</h3><p data-lines=\\\"2\\\" data-type=\\\"br\\\" data-sign=\\\"br2\\\">&nbsp;</p><p data-lines=\\\"1\\\" data-type=\\\"p\\\" data-sign=\\\"1bc7bc84fab52878c330af74c49b925d1\\\">This portfolio is built using <strong>React</strong> and <strong>Three.js</strong>, with a strong focus on <strong>particle effects</strong>. Each section of the website (About, Projects, Experience, Contact) is represented by a <strong>3D particle model</strong>. When navigating between sections, the model smoothly transforms into a new shape, giving the impression of fluid transitions.</p><p data-lines=\\\"2\\\" data-type=\\\"p\\\" data-sign=\\\"11efd2ef4f3f1735c795343b780d7ac42\\\">This makes the site not only functional but also visually dynamic, reflecting my technical background and passion for design.</p><h3 data-lines=\\\"2\\\" data-sign=\\\"9f40c1dd6ac6db640a3c2a2b61ba8e18\\\" id=\\\"%E2%9C%A8-key-features\\\"><a href=\\\"#%E2%9C%A8-key-features\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\"></a>✨ Key Features</h3><p data-lines=\\\"2\\\" data-type=\\\"br\\\" data-sign=\\\"br2\\\">&nbsp;</p><ul class=\\\"cherry-list__default\\\" data-sign=\\\"3f7e0e4e87bb09f38587a512af968afb\\\" data-lines=\\\"9\\', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":35}', 0, NULL, '2025-10-01 15:25:36');
